title: Sobolevsky District
text: Sobolevsky District () is an administrative and municipal district (<a href="raion">raion</a>) of <a href="Kamchatka%20Krai">Kamchatka Krai</a>, <a href="Russia">Russia</a>, one of the <a href="administrative%20divisions%20of%20Kamchatka%20Krai">eleven</a> in the <a href="krai">krai</a>. It is located in the southwest of the krai. The area of the district is . Its <a href="administrative%20center">administrative center</a> is the <a href="types%20of%20inhabited%20localities%20in%20Russia">rural locality</a> ("a <a href="village%23Russia">selo</a>") of <a href="Sobolevo%2C%20Kamchatka%20Krai">Sobolevo</a>. Population: The population of Sobolevo accounts for 68.1% of the district's total population.
